target		<http://example.com/organizing_committee/{ID}> a sigkddstructured-100:Organizing_Committee ; sigkddstructured-100:hasCommittee <http://example.com/conference/{hasCommittee_Inv}> ; sigkddstructured-100:isCommitteeOf <http://example.com/conference/{isCommitteeOf}> . 
